Revision history for Perl extension Data::Validator

1.07 2014-07-17T14:05:12Z
    [BUG FIXES]
    - Fix a wrong expansion in the case of the last optional hashref (#7 robario)

1.06 2014-07-15T13:19:35Z
    [NEW FEATURES]
    - Add Data::Validator::Role::SmartSequenced (#5 robario)

1.04 2013-11-26T13:34:13Z
    [BUG FIXES]
    - Fix an issue that sharing parameters threw cryptic errors
      (@hirobanex++)

1.03 2013-06-11T07:09:44Z
    [FEATURES]
    - Add Data::Validator::Role::NoRestricted not to make the args restricted
     (thanks to keigow for the request)

1.02 2012-11-26 16:23:33
    [DOCUMENT]
    - fix documents about StrictSequenced

1.01 2012-11-26 15:43:11
    [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGE]
    - Named-style arguments are NOT available in StrictSequenced since this version (karupanerura)

1.00 2012-10-20 20:58:51
    - Bump version to 1.00.
    - No feature changes. Just upgrade Module::Install.

0.09 2012-02-16 16:23:07
    - Add StrictSequenced role (karupanerura)

0.08 2011-06-19 21:19:51
    - No code changes
    - Fix tests for latest Moose

0.07 2011-06-03 00:38:00
    - No code changes
    - Now API is considered stable

0.06 2010-11-16 15:57:33
    - Just cleaning up

0.05 2010-11-13 17:49:23
    - Add 'coerce' attribute for rules (default to true)
    - Documentation improvements

0.04 2010-11-13 10:12:07
    - Default to confess(), not croak()
    - Add two extentions: Croak and NoThrow

0.03 2010-11-12 20:24:25
    - Change error handling to report all the errors at once

0.02 2010-11-12 17:36:33
    - No functionality changes
    - Fix error messages
    - Improve documents

